&lt;h2&gt;Gavin DeGuire&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Due: 10/30&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Chapter 4: 29, 33, 35, 37, 38, 40, 61&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/Screenshot-2025-10-29-at-10.15.30-PM.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As given in eqn. 4.17, the radial equation reads:
$$
\frac{1}{R} \frac{d}{dr}\left( r^{2} \frac{dR}{dr} \right) - \frac{2mr^{2}}{\hbar^{2}}[V(r)-E] = \ell(\ell+1)
$$&lt;/p&gt;
